lyTime":"2020-12-14T11:31:26.000Z","msg":"咁屌咗先"},{"pid":"3b586a443ec2f579e5a2e773c06e310d9a840b60","tid":2325030,"uid":370062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"663ac05ec393bf00019d49403c67378801caa589","tid":2325030,"uid":373951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T11:12:56.000Z","msg":"如題<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T11:33:48.000Z","msg":"睇下佢同你傾計嗰陣有冇濕"},{"pid":"b57b80bbe26ee359206613c2aff8b125677af73f","tid":2325030,"uid":246764,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"663ac05ec393bf00019d49403c67378801caa589","tid":2325030,"uid":373951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T11:12:56.000Z","msg":"如題<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T11:35:47.000Z","msg":"想知，易過借火。<br />\n首先你須要一部電話，勃個輪打俾佢，同佢講好唔開心，想搵人傾下計，約係一個月黑風高嘅晚上，係河邊或者公園之類無人打擾嘅地方見面。<br />\n岀於同情心，條女點都會話好啦，就可憐下你呢個小淫蟲。<br />\n好啦，岀到黎，咩都唔洗講，齋行。<br />\n佢問咩都好，唔好答。<br />\n時間一分一秒咁過，終於過左半個鐘，前面嘅舖陳就係為咗下面呢一句，記住要望住佢對眼，帶點憂傷眼神，只有咁樣先可以進可攻退可守，問佢，你中唔中意我？呢一句直擊佢個心，腦海空白，即時小鹿亂撞。咩都唔好講，就等佢一個答案。<br />\n大佬，中意固然，唔中意可以點，咪話我都知無人親近我無人爭奪我囉。"},{"pid":"a91df13e31b2b06d9a65eb87ae7fc2cd0a08fdc2","tid":2325030,"uid":373951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"07243d93b87f0085c25a23359899fe87eb2a6b3f","tid":2325030,"uid":33874,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a896ade052ffabb2c6998ea71bbe11dd1b89627b","tid":2325030,"uid":373951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f15fc8ec23d62a946287c9993da2caa7ef64c43c","tid":2325030,"uid":79117,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T11:14:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T11:17:56.000Z","msg":"即係點 一分鐘前中意 一分鐘後唔中意?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T11:31:26.000Z","msg":"咁屌咗先"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T11:42:57.000Z","msg":"唔好諗咁多呢D<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eefa